messages.messageBody:
> Hi Julie! Haven't talked to you in a while! Good to hear you're
> still on the list. Zena still talks about Japanese silky Bantam
> chickens! LOL
>
> Take care!
> Angie

Hi there.. nice to find you again.. we had a major computer crash a few
months ago and I lost my email addresses and everything else I had
saved..bummer. Anyway, I still have a few Silkies, but I'm actually thinking
of selling them all this year (or finding them a good home) I have a lot
more Standard size chickens now, starting a small egg business..I also
bought a a couple of White Peking Ducks this Spring... Still hoping you all
get a chance to take that road trip and come for a visit sometime!
Julie in MO
